reviewText: My Dad (Don Donovan) was in this movie. Sure it was the best movie but I really need to get a copy of this. My Father passed away in 2010, I really need a copy!

I bought it because Jim Beaman is a local man who got a bit part in a very bad movie.  It claims to be a true story, but they didn't even have the location right as Alfred Packer did his dirty deed (or so he was accused) near Lake City, CO, not Breckenridge.  The movie has no redeeming value.
